strings: <voice_0x01001330><se_def>Black and white: First and foremost, I want to talk about Malta.
<voice_0x01001331><se_def>Black and white: I don't want to hide I don't have time to talk to you and mom.
<voice_0x01001332><se_def>Black and white: I look forward to taking care of him. Otherwise, I'll have to pick up the trash in the back of the house.
<voice_0x01001333><se_def>Black and white: Would you like to know why I live here? ... to be honest, I left the house ... with my mother.
<voice_0x01001334><se_def>Black and white: you are a wise woman I will use everything I have learned from him. when i'm on a mountain i can't
<voice_0x01001335><se_def>Black and white: So I decided to go. I'm here to help you deliver the herbs to Orkutsk.
<voice_0x01001336><se_def>Black and white: I helped them out a lot, so I'm sure they'll be very happy. But I still feel guilty about leaving your mom alone.
<voice_0x01001337><se_def>Black and white: He came to me today with a bag of weed.
<voice_0x01001338><se_def>Black and white: Words cannot express my happiness. I think I finally accepted my choice.
<voice_0x01001339><se_low>King of tricks: As parents, we always look out for our children and do our best when problems arise.
<voice_0x0100133A><se_low>King of tricks: But you're not inviting us here to share your stories. If I'm not mistaken, I have to ask you for help.
<voice_0x0100133B><se_def>Black and white: Sorry, you're right, I'm worried about your mother.
<voice_0x0100133C><se_def>Black and white: I heard a strange sound, like a wolf attacking...?
<voice_0x0100133D><se_def>Black and white: He said that in my veins I have the blood of the Saint. But I do not. People choose who to find someone else.
<voice_0x0100133E><se_def>Black and white: My ancestors were very intelligent. One of the sages who sealed hell.
<voice_0x0100133F><se_def>Black and white: My mother and I are still going this way. If the prince wasn't here...
<voice_0x01001340><se_def>Black and white: I'm worried about your safety. So I decided to go and see him, to see if he was okay.
<voice_0x01001341><se_def>Black and white: And here I would like to ask for your help. If you want to come, I'm a bit afraid to go alone.
<voice_0x01001345><se_def>Black and white: Why don't you give it a try? Thank you everyone! If we hurry! We must leave now.
